question: What are the generic versions of Viagra
ideal_answer: Sildenafil Citrate and Elonza in Thailand are the generic versions of Viagra

snippets.text: generic sildenafil (Unison Laboratories, Thailand) was proved to have the same bioequivalent as in the original formula. The authors conducted a 12-week case series to study the efficacy and safety of Elonza (generic sildenafil)
